## Methodology
- AB significance: paired t-test on daily M1/UV, α=0.05.
- SRM check: chi-square, α=0.001 (industry standard).
- SRM remediation: re-run with `active_visitor_flag='Y'` when raw SRM fails.
- SEO DiD: variant pre/post % change minus control pre/post % change, day-normalized.

Full HTML report: `combined_report.html`.
